<h1>Wallet-Based Agent Payments</h1>

<p>Wallet-based systems hold funds and release them when work completes.</p>

<h2>What this usually means</h2>
<p>Clear tracking of what ran and what was paid.</p>

<h2>What happens next</h2>
<p>Balances update after completed jobs.</p>

<h2>When a human gets involved</h2>
<p>Funding issues or disputes.</p>

<h2>When not to use this</h2>
<p>Complex financial arrangements.</p>

<h2>Risks and limits</h2>
<p>Poor visibility can cause confusion.</p>

